title: gabriel_dateline_1998_web.mp4
description: In 1998 Dateline NBC aired a special report on Gabriel of Sedona/Urantia and the cultish aspects of his Aquarian Concept Community. Not only did they interview Gabriel and several ex-members of the community, but they had two undercover reporters join the commune with hidden cameras over a period of three months. The groups lawyer has been actively attempting to suppress this video on the web:
